Path: godot/tutorials/navigation/navigation_debug_tools.rst  
Summary: This section covers the use of navigation debug tools in Godot, which are only available in debug builds.  

Note: The debug tools, properties and functions are only available in Godot debug builds. Do not use any of them in code that will be part of a release build.
